name: Supermario html5
tagline: Just another Super Mario HTML5 game...
body:
### Welcome Super Mario HTML5 !
You can get the Super Mario HTML5 GitHub reposity , open Terminal (in linux and type:

```
$ mkdir testfile/supermario_html5
$ cd testfile/supermario_html5
$ git github.com/AidePC/SuperMario_html5.git
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync this repository .

### Authors and Contributors
This game is created by @drfarfar and @aidePC

### Support or Contact
You can contact Super Mario HTML5 creators using this email : contact@aidepc.tk
